   <head>[EPITAPH] FOR G. H. Esq;</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The poor man weeps — here G—N sleeps,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Whom canting wretches blam'd:</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But with such as he, where'er he be,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">May I be sav'd or d—'d!</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
